ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT (KAHKEWISTAHAW) which would add to it the name Kahkewistahaw First Nation along with the name of its governing body and a description of the lands where the Kahkewistahaw goods and services tax law would apply.
